The virus is particularly dangerous because it is difficult to detect and remove. Unlike traditional viruses, Jailbreak does not rely on traditional methods of spreading, such as email attachments or malicious websites. Instead, it spreads through a combination of social engineering and advanced coding techniques, making it nearly impossible to prevent.

